#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 17. Assaddhasaṃsandanasutta → assaddhasuttaṃ (bj) | asaddha (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn14.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Assaddhasaṃsandanasutta "
msgstr "17. Faithless "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.159, sc1
msgctxt "sn14.17:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn14.17:1.2"
msgid "“Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, sentient beings come together and converge because of an element: "

#. VAR: Assaddhā → asaddhā (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn14.17:1.3"
msgid "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; "
msgstr "the faithless with the faithless, "

msgctxt "sn14.17:1.4"
msgid "ahirikā ahirikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; "
msgstr "the shameless with the shameless, "

msgctxt "sn14.17:1.5"
msgid "anottappino anottappīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; "
msgstr "the imprudent with the imprudent, "

msgctxt "sn14.17:1.6"
msgid "appassutā appassutehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; "
msgstr "the uneducated with the uneducated, "

msgctxt "sn14.17:1.7"
msgid "kusītā kusītehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; "
msgstr "the lazy with the lazy, "

msgctxt "sn14.17:1.8"
msgid "muṭṭhassatino muṭṭhassatīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; "
msgstr "the unmindful with the unmindful, "

msgctxt "sn14.17:1.9"
msgid "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. "
msgstr "and the witless with the witless. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn14.17:2.1"
msgid "Atītampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu. "
msgstr "In the past, too, sentient beings came together and converged because of an element. … "

msgctxt "sn14.17:2.2"
msgid "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṃ saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu; "
msgstr " "

